column5: The 5:oclock am news this morning is warning that the ice breaker will be working in the Midland habour today to allow a heavy frieghter to make its way into the great lakes . Heads up if your heading out on the ice in that area .
Thanks for the heads up Skip!
Same thing every year.. just when it's safe to start fishing the Sound this little boat comes around. I'm sure he'll be back in Feb to really make a mess.
so we can troll for big pike
